      "notes": "The next two parameters influence the automatic creation of emphasis points within the amplitude envelope.\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/emphasisparameters.png\" />\n\n\n\n**Sensitivity**\nControls how many emphasis points are added to the haptic clip. These points highlight dynamic changes in the audio, they can either replace short amplitude spikes or add texture to a longer modulation.\n\n/newpage\n**Envelope Reduction**\nAdjusts the intensity of the surrounding amplitude at each emphasis point.\n\nA low reduction value blends the emphasis point into the envelope more subtly, while a high reduction makes it stand out more prominently.\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n<video width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/envelopereduction.mp4\" autoplay loop/>\n\n",
