      "notes": "<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 8px;\">\n<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/intro.png\" /></p>\n\nIn this tutorial, you'll learn how to create <b>Haptics from Audio</b>. \n\nAudio to Haptics is a fast workflow that transforms audio assets into high quality haptic feedback by analyzing the audio signal and generating vibration patterns.\n\nLet’s get started!\n"
